title: 190: NFL Jenga Pieces
itunes:title: 190: NFL Jenga Pieces
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are joined by Matt "Money" Smith and Dave Dameshek to go team by team and debate which player or coach each franchise cannot afford to lose. The guys also answer a couple of questions from the #MeUndiesMailbag.
